35 WHEREAS, the youth organization sponsored by the Georgia Prince Hall Masons, the
36 Knights of Pythagoras, provides young men with invaluable leadership, community service,
37 and character-building opportunities; and
38 WHEREAS, the Knights of Pythagoras has enriched the lives of many young men in
39 Georgia, instilling in them the principles of integrity, honor, and community service.
40 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE SENATE that the members of this body
41 recognize and commend Prince Hall Freemasonry and the Most Worshipful Prince Hall
42 Grand Lodge of Georgia as well as extend best wishes for continued growth and success.
43 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Secretary of the Senate is authorized and directed
44 to make an appropriate copy of this resolution available for distribution to the Most
45 Worshipful Prince Hall Grand Lodge of Georgia.
